    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Clive. I believe that we of noble birth have a duty to use our strength to bring peace to the land.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "Royalty, fighting on the front lines? A ruler must risk everything, it seems. In Zofia, we forgot that long ago...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I fight as part of the Deliverance. We will take back Zofia from Desaix's unjust rule—no matter what.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I see your consideration for your comrades. You are kind and diligent in your duties. May I rely on you, too?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'd love to learn more about this world. Your perspective would be of particular value—if you have the time.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I was just taking care of my horse. With no attendants here, the task falls to me. It's a lot of work, but I enjoy it.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Ah, <Player Name>, is it? I bring with me the faith and respect of <Friend Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "This power propels us to the realization of our ideals!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I must continue to devote myself to training...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "You have my apologies. I have failed to meet your expectations.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I shall take this power and deliver victory to you!",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "It's strange. As soon as I see you, I feel the tension that has built up within me crumble into nothing. As a knight commander, I always strive to embody the qualities of a leader. It is my station. Between us, however...I'll admit that I have sometimes thought about casting all of it away. I have never spoken to anyone about this, you must understand. You...are someone I can confide in. I feel I can tell you just about anything. Why is this? Perhaps it is because we hail from different worlds, and different walks of life... Though that may be true...that is not the whole truth. It's your charisma. You charm us all... And we follow you, both on and off the battlefield. That's how I see it.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
